PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778083869
OL,3,C82-year-old woman criticises
OL,4,C'stressful' order to repaint bright
OL,5,Cblue house
OL,7,FAn 82-year-old woman from Deal, in
OL,8,FKent, has said she's finding it 'very
OL,9,Fstressful' after being told to repaint
OL,10,Fher bright blue home.
OL,12,FMary Kenny told ITV Meridian that
OL,13,Fshe's been given 6 months by Dover
OL,14,FDistrict Council to repaint her house,
OL,15,Fas it didn't fit in with other houses
OL,16,Fin the area.
OL,18,FShe had spent more than #3,000
OL,19,Fpainting her house blue in 2023
OL,20,Fbecause she thought similar nearby
OL,21,Fhouses looked pretty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
