OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778083869
OL,3,C82-year-old woman criticises
OL,4,C'stressful' order to repaint bright
OL,5,Cblue house
OL,7,FMs Kenny explained: "It took three
OL,8,Fweeks to paint and nobody objected at
OL,9,Fall, most people said they liked it.
OL,11,F"And then sometime later I heard from
OL,12,Fthe council that there'd been a
OL,13,Fcomplaint by a neighbour."
OL,15,FIt was that complaint that first
OL,16,Fprompted Dover District Council (DDC)
OL,17,Fto contact Ms Kenny in 2024.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778083869
OL,3,C82-year-old woman criticises
OL,4,C'stressful' order to repaint bright
OL,5,Cblue house
OL,7,FThe authority initially advised her to
OL,8,Frepaint her home either white or pale
OL,9,Fcream, but has since taken enforcement
OL,10,Faction.
OL,12,FMrs Kenny has now reluctantly started
OL,13,Fto cooperate, after being told she has
OL,14,Fsix months to comply with the
OL,15,Fcouncil's order, but still hopes
OL,16,Fshe'll be granted an appeal.
OL,18,FShe also feels the council owes her an
OL,19,Fexplanation as to why the colour is
OL,20,Finappropriate, explaining that Deal is
OL,21,Fhome to many colourful properties.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778083869
OL,3,C82-year-old woman criticises
OL,4,C'stressful' order to repaint bright
OL,5,Cblue house
OL,7,F"They don't explain why it's alright
OL,8,Fto paint your house yellow, or brown,
OL,9,For mushroom, but not blue.
OL,11,F"The reasons are cloaked in secrecy
OL,12,Fand it's that lack of openness with
OL,13,Fthe council which I really feel needs
OL,14,Fto be addressed to some extent.
OL,16,FMrs Kenny says she has received
OL,17,Fsupport from her neighbours and is now
OL,18,Fplanning to challenge the council's
OL,19,Fnotice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778083869
OL,3,C82-year-old woman criticises
OL,4,C'stressful' order to repaint bright
OL,5,Cblue house
OL,7,FShe added: "I do find it very
OL,8,Fstressful, I have all sorts of health
OL,9,Fissues."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Dover District Council
OL,12,Fsaid: "The site is within the Middle
OL,13,FDeal Conservation Area, where
OL,14,Fpermitted development rights relating
OL,15,Fto painting of masonry or other
OL,16,Fwalling material have been removed for
OL,17,Felevations fronting a highway.
OL,19,F"This means that planning permission
OL,20,Fwas required for these works which has
OL,21,Fnot been sought.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
