OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1778083869
OL,3,C82-year-old woman criticises
OL,4,C'stressful' order to repaint bright
OL,5,Cblue house
OL,7,F"The decision to issue an enforcement
OL,8,Fnotice was made as the painting of the
OL,9,Fdwelling was considered visually
OL,10,Funsympathetic to the character of the
OL,11,Fconservation area."
